               <p>429. 
               
                  <persName id="t17770702-24-defend206" type="defendantName">
                     JOSEPH
                      GREEN
                  <interp inst="t17770702-24-defend206" type="surname" value="GREEN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-24-defend206" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-24-defend206" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17770702-24-off103" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770702-24-off103" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770702-24-off103" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a cloth coat, value 6 s. a linen shirt, value 2 s. a pair of worsted stockings, value 2 d. a silk handkerchief, value 2 s. and a cheque linen apron, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17770702-24-victim208" type="victimName">
                           Thomas
                            Danaly
                        <interp inst="t17770702-24-victim208" type="surname" value="Danaly"></interp>
